{"type": "article", "id": 29834, "title": "简约的手表", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-19T23:03:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160719221954K9Lfz3IFqBt8nWVE.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>成立于 2014 年的独立工作室 <a href=\"https://www.linjer.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Linjer</a> 一直以制作精美的皮革包而闻名，最近它将产品线扩展到了腕表，推出了“极简”和“经典”两种系列。它们的设计灵感均来源于奥斯陆歌剧院这一地标建筑，简单的线条以及漂亮的大理石元素都颇受旗下设计师的青睐。以此为出发点，他们设计出了简约、不带 logo 的手表：选用水晶玻璃和不锈钢打造外壳，内置来自瑞士有着高精准度的 Ronda 5 机芯。表带则采用植鞣革制成，会随着使用染上时间的痕迹，调换也非常方便。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1474018119/minimalist-watches-without-the-luxury-markup\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 159 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719222217wYcdVI8RWi2FEXQG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.688235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719222145WlLsTcaiR7563Zfp.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747059\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607192221456zTUDaNZyL0Qm1bI.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.951471\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719222145fTG6Sbi5docnFVvm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}